title: Western Warriors SC
text:
Western Warriors Soccer Club is a <a href="association%20football">football</a> club based in <a href="Nassau%2C%20Bahamas">Nassau</a>, <a href="Bahamas">Bahamas</a>. They play in the <a href="BFA%20Senior%20League">BFA Senior League</a>.
Achievements.
<a href="BFA%20Senior%20League">BFA Senior League</a>: 2
<a href="New%20Providence%20FA%20Cup">New Providence FA Cup</a>: 2
